title: For Sale:  Picture Frame Gun Safe
postcontent:
The problem with most gun safes is the balance between keeping your gun safe and out of reach from children while maintaining quick access!  Usually this means spending a pretty penny for a quick access safe with combinations, finger prints, etc.  Not a bad option, but I found them hard to hide in the middle of your house in plain view.  So I started building my own!  These picture frame safes are perfect for easy access right under everyone’s radar.  No one even knows it's there.  That's the best security you can ask for.
The cabinet pictured above is pretty standard with soft close hinges, magnetic gun mount, and is drilled for adjustable shelves.  But I can offer any option you can imagine.  This cabinet does not lock but I can add locking hardward if desired.
What I would like to offer is custom cabinets that fit your needs.  Whatever size you would like.  For any application. 
I can build these cabinets with hinged doors or sliding doors for bigger cabinets.  They can range from small cabinets, just big enough for a hand gun to larger units, big enough for shotgun or rifle.
I'm not offering a standard base model at this point.  I am interested in building a custom cabinet for you!
 
Pricing will depend on what you are looking for and what options you would like.
Just contact me and I can get some drawings pulled together and let you know pricing.
